| \`color.textOnPrimary\` | color | semantic | #FFFFFF | Text/icon color on primary surfaces. |
| \`color.transparent\` | color | semantic | transparent | No fill — e.g. ghost button background. |
| \`duration.fast\` | duration | semantic | 150ms | Hover/press micro-interactions. |
| \`easing.standard\` | easing | semantic | cubic-bezier(0.2, 0, 0, 1) | Default easing for UI transitions. |
