| \`palette.blue.700\` | color | primitive | #1E3FA0 |  |
| \`palette.red.600\` | color | primitive | #C0341D |  |
| \`palette.slate.300\` | color | primitive | #C4C9D1 |  |
| \`palette.slate.900\` | color | primitive | #181A1D |  |
